 Comics|Marvel.com]]|first=Marc|last=Strom|date=July 5, 2017|accessdate=July 5, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6rjsXF6gD?url=https://news.marvel.com/tv/68147/mustafa-shakir-gabrielle-dennis-join-netflix-original-series-marvels-luke-cage/|archivedate=July 5, 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ColterJul2017\">{{cite web|url=https://screenrant.com/luke-cage-season-2-mike-colter-writing/|title=Luke Cage Season 2 Will Be Exciting, Relevant & Pop Culture-Heavy|last=Mohamed|first=Jasmine|publisher=Screen Rant|date=July 21, 2017|accessdate=July 22, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6s8jLkNa7?url=http://screenrant.com/luke-cage-season-2-mike-colter-writing/|archivedate=July 22, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"EpCount\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/07/the-defenders-luke-cage-marvel-netflix-new-york-state-productions-tax-credits-largest-ever-1202139332/|title=Marvel TV-Netflix New York Projects Will Count 135 Episodes By Year\u2019s End; Record Production Commitment In State\u2019s History|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=July 31, 2017|accessdate=July 31, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6sNVPPuk8?url=http://deadline.com/2017/07/the-defenders-luke-cage-marvel-netflix-new-york-state-productions-tax-credits-largest-ever-1202139332/|archivedate=July 31, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CokerMoreMusic\">{{cite web|url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/09/28/netflixs-luke-cage-show-creator-says-we-are-the-best-music-show-on-television-6156492/|title=Netflix\u2019s Luke Cage show creator says: \u2018We are the best music show on television\u2019|last=Duff|first=Seamus|publisher=[[Metro.co.uk]]|date=September 28, 2016|accessdate=August 14, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6sgZBVe1m?url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/09/28/netflixs-luke-cage-show-creator-says-we-are-the-best-music-show-on-television-6156492/|archivedate=August 13, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ColterJul2017Music\">{{cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/2017/07/22/luke-cage-season-2-storyline-soundtrack-netflix-sdcc-2017/|title=Mike Colter Excited For Luke Cage Season 2 Soundtrack, Storyline|last=Jackson|first=Dallas|publisher=ComicBook.com|date=July 22, 2017|accessdate=August 14, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6sgZGisO2?url=http://comicbook.com/marvel/2017/07/22/luke-cage-season-2-storyline-soundtrack-netflix-sdcc-2017/|archivedate=August 13, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Comanche\">{{cite web|url=http://www.blackfilm.com/read/2017/08/thomas-q-jones-reprise-comanche-role-luke-cage-season-2/|title=Thomas Q. Jones To Reprise Comanche Role In Luke Cage Season 2|last=Morales|first=Wilson|publisher=Black Film|date=August 31, 2017|accessdate=August 31, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6t8VACriV?url=http://www.blackfilm.com/read/2017/08/thomas-q-jones-reprise-comanche-role-luke-cage-season-2/|archivedate=August 31, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Jones\">{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/tv/2017/10/04/marvel-luke-cage-season-2-iron-fist-photo/|title=Marvel's Luke Cage first look: Iron Fist joins Luke in season 2|last=Li|first=Shirley|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|date=October 4, 2017|accessdate=October 4, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6tyYjy2RD?url=http://ew.com/tv/2017/10/04/marvel-luke-cage-season-2-iron-fist-photo/|archivedate=October 5, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ColterIF\">{{cite web|url=http://www.blackfilm.com/read/2017/10/exclusive-mike-colter-talks-girls-trip-blu-ray-luke-cage-season-2/|title=Exclusive: Mike Colter Talks Girls Trip Blu-ray & Luke Cage Season 2|last=Morales|first=Wilson|publisher=BlackFilm.com|date=October 16, 2017|accessdate=October 17, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6v8ORUaL3?url=http://www.blackfilm.com/read/2017/10/exclusive-mike-colter-talks-girls-trip-blu-ray-luke-cage-season-2/|archivedate=November 21, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref nam